            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Closed by https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/33036\n\nSince https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/33036 decided to reflect the literal default value of 'statusline' (instead of special-casing), the original motivation for this issue no longer applies. \n\nIt's now possible to simply do:\n\n```lua\nvim.print(vim.api.nvim_eval_statusline(vim.api.nvim_get_option_info2('statusline', {}).default, {}))\n```",
